## الخطوات العملية

### 1. WebSocket Analysis
```bash
# Intercept WebSocket في Burp Suite
# Proxy → WebSocket history
# أو بـ wscat
wscat -c ws://10.10.2.50/ws
# أي message تتسجلها = real-time SCADA data!
```

### 2. WebSocket Manipulation
```bash
# إرسال message للـ server
wscat -c ws://10.10.2.50/ws
> {"type":"setpoint","room":101,"value":999}
# لو الـ server قبلها = RCE via WebSocket!
```

### 3. الإصلاح
```javascript
// Server-side WebSocket authentication
const wss = new WebSocket.Server({
  verifyClient: (info, callback) => {
    const token = new URL(info.req.url, 'ws://localhost').searchParams.get('token');
    try {
      const payload = jwt.verify(token, SECRET_KEY);
      info.req.user = payload;
      callback(true);
    } catch {
      callback(false, 401, 'Unauthorized');
    }
  }
});

// Use WSS not WS
const wss = new WebSocket.Server({
  server: httpsServer,  // HTTPS server
  // All traffic encrypted
});
```

